Class StringPropertyTest

java.lang.Object
  net.sourceforge.pmd.properties.AbstractPropertyDescriptorTester
      net.sourceforge.pmd.properties.StringPropertyTest

public class StringPropertyTest
extends AbstractPropertyDescriptorTester

Evaluates the functionality of the StringProperty descriptor by testing its ability to catch creation errors (illegal args), flag invalid strings per any specified expressions, and serialize/deserialize groups of strings onto/from a string buffer.

Author:
Brian Remedios
